Texts.Chs: 一顿美餐。。。至少对于那些喜欢在科技发展部前嬉戏的人来说是这样。
Texts.Eng: A fine meal... For those cozying up to the Miniknog, at least.

Texts.Chs: 一顿美味的大餐。假设你能把壳取下来，就是这样。
Texts.Eng: A purty fancy meal. Assumin' you can get that shell off, that is.

Texts.Chs: 与王储的任何相似之处纯属巧合。
Texts.Eng: Any resemblance to crown princes are purely coincidental.

Texts.Chs: 即使在死亡时，这种生物的外壳仍保持着一种奇妙的红色光泽。
Texts.Eng: Even in death, the shell of this creature maintains a marvelous red sheen.

Texts.Chs: 我怀疑很多有问题的农民在他们的有生之年从未见过这么好的一顿饭。
Texts.Eng: I doubt many Glitch peasants have ever seen such a fine meal in their lifetimes.

Texts.Chs: 也许我能用我的喙把壳敲开？
Texts.Eng: Perhaps I can crack the shell open with my beak?
